                    Transparent pricing for Decatur and Morgan County:
                </p>

                <div class="bg-[#FFA985]/10 p-6 rounded-xl mb-8">
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-700 mb-0">
                        <li>
                            <strong
                                ><a
                                    href="/locations/decatur/recurring-maid-service"
